-- Russia debt insurance costs hit Nov 2011 highs
-- 
-- Mon Apr 28, 2014 04:08AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, April 28 (Reuters) - The cost of insuring Russia's debt against default hit its highest since Nov 2011 on Monday on increasing tensions over Ukraine and worries about further sanctions against Russia.

U.S. President Barack Obama said the United Staes would announce new sanctions on Russia later today. [ID:nL2N0NK05R]